# No system-level 'ed' symlink is created by this package to avoid conflicts
# with the classic ed(1) line editor (/usr/bin/ed from the 'ed' package).
#
# Users can install a safe alias with:
#   edit --install-alias
# which creates the symlink in the first writable directory from:
#   ~/.local/bin   /opt/bin   /usr/local/bin
#
# The postinst script creates /usr/local/bin/ed with full conflict checking.
